---------------------------------------------------------------------------
FREE USE
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

ZANACMS may be used free of charge for:

  * private websites and personal projects
  * educational use
  * non-commercial organisations and non-commercial projects
  * local development, testing and evaluation

A non-commercial organisation does not require a commercial license only
because it has members, donations, public funding or a small operating
budget. A commercial license is required if the website is primarily used
for commercial services, paid client work, business promotion, sales,
marketing or other revenue-generating activities.

Agencies, freelancers and other commercial users may evaluate and test
ZANACMS locally free of charge. A commercial license is required when
ZANACMS is used for paid client work or for a productive commercial website.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
COMMERCIAL USE
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Commercial use requires a valid commercial site license.

Commercial use includes, but is not limited to:

  * company or business websites
  * websites for self-employed professionals
  * client or customer projects
  * agency use and paid client work
  * commercial services built on ZANACMS
  * hosting, resale or white-label use of ZANACMS-based systems

A commercial site license is valid for one productive website.

A productive website is a public or internal live website used for a real
person, organisation, business, client or project. Development, local
testing and staging installations for the same website do not require an
additional license.

One website may include multiple languages, layouts and normal subpages.
Separate websites, separate client projects and separate independently
operated domains require separate licenses.

A commercial site license covers all releases within the same major version,
for example all 2.x releases. A new commercial site license is required for
a new major version.

The license fee is the fee listed at the time of purchase. The current 
license fee is listed at: https://axmann.eu/zcmspricing.php?lg=en 

A commercial site license grants the right to use ZANACMS for the licensed
website. It does not include support, maintenance, custom development,
hosting or guaranteed updates unless agreed separately.

