MODIFICATIONS
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

You may modify ZANACMS for your own permitted use under this license.

Modified versions may not be distributed, sold, sublicensed, rebranded or
offered as a competing CMS product without separate written permission.

If you modify ZANACMS for a licensed commercial website, the commercial
site license applies to that website only. It does not grant the right to
redistribute ZANACMS or modified versions of ZANACMS as a separate product.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
RESTRICTIONS
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Without separate written permission, the following is not permitted:

  * reselling or sublicensing ZANACMS itself
  * distributing ZANACMS as part of a competing CMS product
  * offering ZANACMS itself as a hosted CMS service
  * distributing modified versions under the ZANACMS name
  * removing or altering copyright, author or license notices from the
    ZANACMS source code or distribution files

